    "abstract": "<jats:title>Abstract</jats:title>\n                <jats:p>RNA extraction has become a bottleneck for detection of COVID-19, in part because of reagent shortages. We present here a rapid protocol that circumvents the need for RNA extraction that is compatible with RT-qPCR-based detection methods.</jats:p>",
